description:
She`s a third year student whose unique traits are her pearl white hair and her crimson eyes. She has an ample bosom belying her delicate frame. She`s plotting Raishin`s assassination for certain reasons, but she`s kind at heart and she often fails due to her clumsiness. She manipulates Rabbi, one the Gram series automatons developed by D-Works. She`s Loki`s older sister.
Source: ANN
name: Frey
